Instalation instructions for wessie - web site system
=====================================================

Document version: $Id$

1. download latest wessie version
2. untar/unzip it into some directory that can be viewed through web
3. check whether you have all required software to run wessie:
     - PHP => 4.0.4pl1
     - MySQL => 3.23.23
4. create mysql database that will wessie use and add there user - for example
   by using following SQL commands:

   CREATE TABLE wessie;
   GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON wessie.* to wessie@localhost IDENTIFIED BY 'wessie';

